Shaman
Base Mechanic Adjustment
-Gains a mana ability that reduces the merge rank of the highest-rank shaman.
-Ability cannot reduce a unit below merge rank 1.
-Cooldown left for developers to define

1st Talent (Left) Fox’s Blessing: A new variant of the shaman is introduced called the Chief ritualist (first shamans merged don't result in a curse but create a Chief Ritualist) With the chief ritualist in the center of the board and 4 shamans at each corner all with a combined merge rank of 15. For 25s The Shamans conducts a blessing thank increases the mergerank of 2 units adjacent to the Ritualist by 1(The shamans must not be merged or disturbed during the ritual or it'll cause a restart)
1st Talent (Right) Fox’s Curse: A new variant of the shaman is introduced called the Chief Ritualist, WIth the chief ritualist in the center of the board and 4 shamans at each corner all with a combined merge rank of 15. For 40s the Shamans conducts a curse on the opponent that reduces the merge rank of units of the units in the two marked squares on the opponent’s board by 2.The squares are randomized after each successful ritual (The shamans must not be merged or disturbed during the ritual or it'll cause a restart)
*sound cues to show the initiation of a ritual and disruption*

2nd Talent (Left) Loved by the goddess: After a successful ritual each unit has a 3% chance for 1st talent to change merge rank by 2 and 0.5% chance to change merge rank by 3
2nd Talent (Right) A believers Faith: Merging other units have a 3% chance to activate the shaman’s basic mechanic.

3rd Talent (Left) Totem of Great Fortune: Throws a totem on the path before the Phantom, which lasts 30 seconds. The totem has a 5% chance of canceling a bosses a effect by the power of the goddess
3rd Talent (Right) Venge Totem of Calamity: Throws a totem on the opponents path during the Phantom, which lasts 30 seconds. The totem has a 2.5% chance of doubling bosses effect by the power of the goddess

Final Talent:Deity of Reality: Every wave a shaman has a 5% chance to be possessed upon summoning.The possessed shaman doesn't attack, once merged with the chief ritualist he becomes enlightened.After the last monster shows up it summons the goddess of reality which descends as two fox spirits; The fox of destruction descends to the opponents board stunning 3 units.The fox of creation creates traps on the ground that slow the boss by 20% then descends unto your highest merge rank unit giving it a 30% damage increase for the duration of the boss wave.

Shaman Reincarnation

Skill 1- ENLIGHTENED SPIRIT (with Dryrad) Possessed shaman and gives 1% crit chance to adjacent units and if in the center of the board he gives 1% crit chance to all units.
L1 at 0.75% Increased critical chance
L2 at 1.00% Increased critical chance
L3 at 1.25% Increased critical chance

Skill 2  -  DEITY’S PUNISHMENT (with Knight Statue) Deity of Reality improved.The fox spirit has a chance to lock opponents hero ability for a duration of time
L1:5% chance of activation for 2.5 seconds
L2:10% chance of activation for 3.5 seconds
L3:15% chance of activation for 5 seconds

Skill 3 - WITCH DOCTOR(with Witch): A chance for an enlightened chief ritualist to remove negative effects from adjacent units
L1: 7% chance to remove negative effects 
L2: 14% chance to remove negative effects 
L3: 20% chance to remove negative effects
